Insider Activity


Individual




Richard J. Berman



Mr. Richard J. Berman is Independent Director at CryoPort, Inc., Chairman at MetaStat, Inc., Chairman at Project Finance LLP, Independent Director at Advaxis, Inc., Independent Director at Caladrius Biosciences, Inc., Chairman at Duncan Capital Financial Group, Inc., Chairman at Candidate Resources, Inc., Chairman at Fortress Technology Systems, Inc., Chairman at Secure Fortress Technology Systems, Inc., and Executive Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Superfly Advertising, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at CryoPort, Inc., BlackRidge Technology Holdings, Inc., Energy Smart Resources, Inc., Advaxis, Inc., Caladrius Biosciences, Inc., Secure Fortress Plc, and Founders Finance LLC.
Mr. Berman was previously employed as Independent Director by Lustros, Inc., Independent Director by QuantumSphere, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Morlex, Inc., Chairman by National Investment Managers, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Internet Commerce Corp., an Advisory Board Member by MTN Capital Partners LLC, Executive Chairman by Superfly Advertising, Inc., a Principal by Goldman Sachs, Inc., Senior Vice President by Bankers Trust Co., Senior Vice President by Bankers Trust Corp., and Senior Vice President by Deutsche Bank Investment Management, Inc. He also served on the board at MediaBay, Inc., NexMed, Inc., Broadcaster, Inc., Dyadic International, Inc., EasyLink Services International Corp., GVI Security Solutions, Inc., International Microcomputer Software, Inc., Nayna Networks, Inc., Way Cool Imports, Inc., Strategic Funding Source, Inc., and Vertical Search Works, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from The Leonard N Stern School of Business, a graduate degree from Boston College, a graduate degree from The Hague Academy of International Law, and an MBA from The Leonard N Stern School of Business.



